longBusinessSummary: Gourmet Ocean Products Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was involved in the production of seed for scallop and sea cucumber for aquaculture farms. The company was also a buyer and exporter of sea cucumber. Gourmet Ocean Products Inc. was founded in 2007 and is based in Calgary, Canada.
